OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fsettled evening with little cloud and
OL,7,Fplenty of evening sunshine. Winds will
OL,8,Fbe light and variable inland.
OL,9,FRemaining mild overnight despite the
OL,10,Flargely clear skies.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA fine and dry day, with
OL,13,Fbright sunshine and light variable
OL,14,Fwinds. Feeling hot, though
OL,15,Ftemperatures could be a degree or two
OL,16,Fcooler along the coast in any sea
OL,17,Fbreezes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
